i%3EUkraine%20and%20Russia%20are%20working%20on%20implementing%20artificial%20intelligence%20into%20their%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20both%20sides%20face%20challenges%20in%20mass-deploying%20that%20capability%2C%20recent%20research%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20has%20been%20some%20limited%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20drones%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20but%20it's%20mostly%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20remains%20largely%20human-operated%20for%20now.%20We're%20seeing%20glimpses%20of%20the%20future%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20there%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20and%20Russia%20are%20experimenting%20with%20artificial%20intelligence-enabled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-drone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20total%20autonomy%20and%20full-scale%20deployment%20remain%20limited%20in%20combat%2C%20researchers%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-enabled%20autonomy%20in%20uncrewed%20systems%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20significantly%20impact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-smart-drones-more-likely-hit-targets-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20drones%20are%20used%20on%20the%20battlefield%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reducing%20the%20strain%20on%20human%20operators%2C%20bypassing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhidden-electronic-warfare-battle-demanding-more-of-ukrainian-soldiers-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelectronic%20warfare%20and%20signal%20jamming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20speeding%20up%20the%20targeting%20and%20decision-making%20process.%20It%20can%20also%20analyze%20data%20and%20adapt%20in%20real%20time%2C%20which%20is%20advantageous%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d107f5d-23e0-4c55-803d-4777599b90b7%5C%22%3ENot%20quite%20autonomous%20and%20not%20being%20used%20at%20scale%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKateryna%20Bondar%2C%20a%20fellow%20in%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20Wadhwani%20AI%20Center%2C%20reported%20in%20March%20that%20autonomy%2C%20a%20system's%20ability%20to%20independently%20operate%20in%20complex%20environments%20with%20limited%20supervision%2C%20isn't%20%26quot%3Byet%20present%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20report%20from%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20expert%20Kateryna%20Stepanenko%20explains%20that%20%26quot%3Bneither%20Russia%20nor%20Ukraine%20has%20leveraged%20AI%2FML%20drones%20on%20the%20battlefield%20at%20scale%20as%20of%20early%20June%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20prepares%20to%20launch%20long-range%20drones%20from%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20February.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68079d3d3fe8d3928363ae3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20face%20challenges%20in%20continuing%20to%20innovate%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20in%20drones.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEvgeniy%20Maloletka%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20both%20sides%20are%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20integrating%20ML%20capabilities%20with%20some%20limited%20AI%20adaptations%20into%20new%20drone%20variants%20on%20the%20path%20to%20developing%20fully%20AI%2FML-powered%20drones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20that%20use%20machine%20learning%2C%20even%20with%20some%20AI%2C%20still%20largely%20require%20involvement%20from%20an%20operator.%20Machine%20learning%20could%20enable%20the%20drones%20to%20perform%20pre-programmed%20tasks%2C%20but%20they%20lack%20the%20autonomy%20a%20true%20AI%20capability%20would%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bd33845-b582-4a70-bd13-71dca675b21d%5C%22%3ENot%20an%20AI%20revolution%2C%20at%20least%20not%20yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20forces%20have%20observed%20Russia%20flying%20drone%20swarms%20that%20rely%20on%20visual%20terrain%20navigation%20%E2%80%94%20which%20uses%20onboard%20cameras%20and%20maps%20instead%20of%20vulnerable%20GPS%20%E2%80%94%20and%20can%20autonomously%20detect%20and%20select%20targets%20without%20operator%20input.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20month%2C%20Ukraine%20said%20it%20deployed%20an%20AI-enabled%20%26quot%3Bmother%20drone%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20autonomously%20send%20first-person%20view%20drones%20to%20strike%20targets.%20And%20the%20Security%20Service%20of%20Ukraine%20reported%20that%20the%20uncrewed%20systems%20used%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-spiderweb-drone-attack-wake-up-call-us-in-pacific-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOperation%20Spiderweb%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Russian%20aircraft%20at%20military%20airbases%20earlier%20this%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foperation-spiderweb-ukraine-drones-ai-hit-russia-planes-lost-signal-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eswitched%20to%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20complete%20their%20mission%20if%20they%20lost%20signal%20with%20the%20operator.%20The%20security%20service%20said%20this%20was%20done%20using%20AI%20algorithms%20and%20manual%20operator%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBondar's%20report%20in%20March%20on%20drones%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20systems%20equipped%20with%20AI%20are%20three%20to%20four%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20hit%20their%20target%20than%20drones%20piloted%20solely%20by%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20has%20the%20revolution%20come%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20commander%20of%20another%20drone%20unit%20said%20last%20fall%20that%20he%20expected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-in-ukraine-war-soon-wont-need-human-pilots-commander-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-enabled%20drones%20that%20didn't%20need%20a%20pilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20on%20the%20battlefield%20within%20six%20months.%20That%20future%20is%20not%20here%20just%20yet.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20front-line%20Ukrainian%20drone%20unit%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffiber-optic-ai-drones-could-radically-change-battlefield-ukraine-operators-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-enabled%20drones%20weren't%20being%20widely%20used%20yet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20become%20a%20proving%20ground%20for%20cheap%20drones%20and%20emerging%20technology%3B%20however%2C%20turning%20prototypes%20into%20a%20scalable%2C%20battlefield-ready%20AI%20fleet%20will%20require%20data%2C%20chips%2C%20and%20coordination%20that%20neither%20side%20fully%20has%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine%20troops%20drones%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631a3dba0a329a0011e3868c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI-enabled%20drones%20can%20relieve%20some%20of%20the%20reliance%20on%20human%20operators%20and%20complete%20many%20tasks%20on%20their%20own.%3Cp%3EWolfgang%20Schwan%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Russia%2C%20Stepanenko%20wrote%2C%20further%20development%20of%20these%20important%20combat%20capabilities%20will%20depend%20on%20gathering%2C%20storing%2C%20and%20managing%20battlefield%20data%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20for%20missions%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20critically%2C%20sorting%20out%20how%20best%20to%20identify%20enemy%20drones%20from%20friendly%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20already%20been%20working%20on%20the%20latter%20with%20situational%20awareness%20systems%20like%20Delta%20and%20Kropyva%2C%20which%20Stepanenko%20reported%20are%20similar%20to%20the%20command%20and%20control%20systems%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20has%20env