E%20are%20improving%2C%20and%20it's%20boosting%20the%20case%20for%20prices%20to%20rise%20from%20here.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20note%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20Mike%20Wilson.%20The%20bank's%20CIO%20and%20chief%20stock%20strategist%20pointed%20to%20a%20key%20signal%20that's%20sending%20a%20bullish%20signal%3A%20a%20sharp%20rebound%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-cutting-guidance-earnings-forecasts-amid-tariffs-economic-uncertainty-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20revisions%20breadth%2C%20or%20the%20proportion%20of%20analysts%20who%20have%20raised%20their%20estimates%20minus%20the%20proportion%20who%20have%20lowered%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indicator%20is%20now%20at%20-10%25%2C%20a%20noticeable%20improvement%20from%20-25%25%20during%20the%20height%20of%20tariff%20uncertainty%20in%20April%2C%20an%20indication%20that%20sentiment%20is%20recovering.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Earnings%20revision%20breadth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6846ff0385e81483682bb297%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221286%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20believes%20the%20indicator%20will%20continue%20to%20trend%20upward.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorgan-stanley-dollar-index-decline-rate-cuts-treasurys-trump-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweak%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20further%20bolster%20this%20earnings%20gauge%2C%20as%20US%20companies%20that%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20business%20overseas%20receive%20a%20boost%20in%20sales%20when%20the%20dollar%20is%20weaker.%20Once%20earnings%20revisions%20breadth%20turns%20positive%2C%20investors%20should%20expect%20forward%20EPS%20predictions%20to%20trend%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnings%20revision%20breadth%20can%20be%20driven%20by%20either%20fewer%20downward%20revisions%20or%20more%20upward%20revisions.%20According%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20the%20latter%20is%20the%20case%20today%2C%20which%20is%20good%20news%20for%20investors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20upward%20revisions%20tend%20to%20result%20in%20stronger%20overall%20stock%20market%20performance%2C%20historically%20leading%20to%20a%2013%25%20increase%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20over%20a%2012-month%20span.%20When%20fewer%20downward%20revisions%20are%20the%20driving%20factor%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20historically%20returned%208%25%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%2012-month%20price%20target%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%206%2C500%2C%20a%20potential%20gain%20of%208%25%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20should%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20improvement%20in%20forward-looking%20earnings%20revision%20breadth%20rather%20than%20lagging%20hard%20data%2C%20according%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley.%20The%20bank%20sees%20April%20stock%20market%20lows%20as%20the%20end%20of%20a%20year-long%20trend%20of%20downward%20earnings%20revisions%2C%20and%20expects%20the%20rate%20of%20change%20on%20earnings%20revision%20breadth%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20driver%20of%20equity%20prices%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20experience%2C%20when%20revisions%20breadth%20is%20accelerating%20in%20a%20V-shaped%20manner%20from%20an%20extreme%20low%2C%20equity%20markets%20typically%20remain%20supported%20and%20pullbacks%20remain%20shallow%20and%20unsatisfying%20(like%20the%20past%206%20weeks)%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20outperformance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-recession-risk-cyclical-defensive-stocks-ratio-valuations-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecyclical%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20points%20to%20a%20market%20more%20focused%20on%20forward-looking%20earnings%20revisions%20than