%22_blank%5C%22%3Einventory%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-warehouse-robots-picking-challenge-2025-2%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewarehouse%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-trucking-logistics-uber-freight-tech-optimize-routes-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelivery%20routes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20US%20universities%20and%20certification%20programs%20are%20incorporating%20tech-focused%20coursework%20into%20existing%20supply%20chain%20management%20lessons%20so%20that%20students%20can%20prepare%20to%20work%20in%20the%20sector's%20up-and-coming%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20companies%20are%20partnering%20directly%20with%20universities%20to%20ensure%20students%20have%20the%20skills%20they%20need%20to%20join%20the%20workforce.%20Blue%20Yonder%2C%20a%20supply%20chain%20software%20provider%2C%20inked%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.blueyonder.com%2Fblue-yonder-and-university-of-arkansas-supply-chain-management-program-announce-strategic-partnership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-year%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20with%20the%20University%20of%20Arkansas%2C%20making%20Blue%20Yonder%20the%20first-ever%20title%20sponsor%20for%20the%20Master%20of%20Science%20in%20Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20program%2C%20the%20university%20uses%20Blue%20Yonder%20technology%20as%20a%20teaching%20tool%2C%20while%20also%20collaborating%20with%20the%20company's%20leaders%20on%20courses%2C%20curriculum%2C%20and%20guest%20lectures.%20Nathalie%20Carruthers%2C%20the%20chief%20associate%20success%20officer%20at%20Blue%20Yonder%2C%20said%20the%20partnership%20goes%20beyond%20securing%20its%20own%20talent%20pipeline%20and%20hoping%20graduates%20might%20work%20for%20the%20company%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20evolving%20the%20practice%20of%20supply%20chain%20as%20a%20discipline%2C%20as%20a%20profession%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20tomorrow's%20supply%20chain%20professionals%20are%20prepared%20for%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20in%20this%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Carruthers%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffbdad19-5eb6-48e0-ad99-63449d69e54f%5C%22%3EA%20new%20kind%20of%20syllabus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday's%20supply%20chain%20programs%20and%20careers%20look%20different%20from%20years%20past.%20In%202000%2C%20there%20were%20about%20a%20dozen%20academic%20supply%20chain%20programs%2C%20said%20Abe%20Eshkenazi%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Association%20for%20Supply%20Chain%20Management%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20supply%20chain%20transformation%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20leadership.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%20700%2C%20with%20pandemic-related%20supply-chain%20issues%20contributing%20to%20more%20awareness%20and%20interest%20in%20the%20career%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20supply%20chain%20workers%20often%20came%20from%20warehousing%20or%20transportation%20backgrounds%20with%20a%20manual%20labor%20focus.%20Now%2C%20warehouse%20roles%20require%20a%20greater%20understanding%20of%20technology%2C%20Carruthers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20has%20affected%20university%20programs%2C%20which%20now%20incorporate%20technology%20to%20prepare%20students%20for%20work%20in%20modern%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20universities%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20willingness%20and%20a%20strong%20interest%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20technology%20piece%20is%20there%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20curricula%2C%20Carruthers%20said.%20Students%20could%20be%20given%20real-life%20case%20studies%2C%20such%20as%20a%20cargo%20ship%20being%20stuck%20in%20the%20Suez%20Canal%2C%20and%20asked%20to%20think%20through%20how%20they%20would%20solve%20the%20issue%20using%20technology%20or%20AI%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVince%20Castillo%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20logistics%20at%20The%20Ohio%20State%20University%20Fisher%20College%20of%20Business%2C%20teaches%20a%20logistics%20and%20supply%20chain%20analytics%20course.%20He%20introduces%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-better-ai-chatgpt-prompts-according-prompt-engineer-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EgenAI%20prompts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ethics%2C%20AI%20assistants%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkraft-heinz-ai-lighthouse-helps-forecast-supply-chain-demands-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epredictive%20analytics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20forecasting%2C%20and%20vehicle%20routing%20with%20AI.%20Students%20build%20a%20machine%20learning%20model%20that%20forecasts%20demand%20or%20studies%20delivery%20challenges%2C%20and%20they%20experiment%20with%20letting%20AI%20write%20the%20code%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20against%20this%20backdrop%20of%20how%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20help%20or%20hinder%20those%20sorts%20of%20analytical%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20Castillo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20teaches%20an%20executive%20education%20class%2C%20designed%20for%20current%20supply%20chain%20professionals.%20During%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffisher.osu.edu%2Fexecutive-education%2Fprograms-individuals%2Fgenerative-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-day%20course%20on%20genAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20attendees%20learn%20AI%20ethics%2C%20practical%20applications%20for%20genAI%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20%E2%80%94%20like%20contract%20analysis%20and%20customer%20relationship%20management%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20to%20implement%20these%20processes%20at%20their%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20for%20Supply%20Chain%20Management%20offers%20several%20supply%20chain%20certifications.%20Technology%20has%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20part%26quot%3B%20of%20some%2C%20Eshkenazi%20said%2C%20including%20the%20Certified%20in%20Planning%20and%20Inventory%20Management%20designation%20and%20the%20Supply%20Chain%20Technology%20Certificate%2C%20both%20of%20which%20include%20lessons%20on%20using%20AI%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emachine%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20asks%20companies%20which%20skills%20they're%20seeking%2C%20which%20then%20informs%20the%20content%20of%20its%20certification%20programs.%20It%20recently%20surveyed%203%2C500%20supply%20chain%20professionals%20and%20found%2045%25%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20chatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20jobs.%20Companies%20are%20beginning%20to%20say%20that%20having%20AI%20and%20technology%20skills%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20nice%20to%20have%3B%20it's%20a%20need%20to%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Eshkenazi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232930838-34de-4bd6-95ec-02a02f1ca33f%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20one%20tool%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20workforce's%20toolkit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20generations%20entering%20university%20are%20digital%20natives%20who%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20tech%2C%20and%20AI%20is%20now%20part%20of%20that.%20Castillo%20said%20that%20during%20the%20most%20recent%20semester%2C%20almost%20every%20student%20in%20his%20class%20had%20an%20AI%20model%20on%20their%20screen%20in%20the%20computer%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20fear%20in%20terms%20of%20new%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Carruthers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20students%20tend%20to%20lack%20critical-thinking%20skills%2C%20Eshkenazi%20said.%20He%20described%20them%20as%20overweight%20on%20technology%20and%20underweight%20on%20problem%20solving%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bblindly%20applying%20technology%20without%20understanding%20the%20implications.%26quot%3B%20He%20likened%20it%20to%20handing%20the%20keys%20of%20a%20Ferrari%20to%20someone%20who%20just%20got%20their%20driver's%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20systems%20are%20much%20more%20powerful%20than%20we're%20using%20them%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Eshkenazi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20associations%2C%20universities%2C%20and%20partner%20companies%20are%20trying%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20teaching%20AI%20and%20business%20skills.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20principles%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hospital-inventory-management-advice-mayo-clinic-cleveland-clinic-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20going%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastillo%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20give%20his%20students%20as%20much%20experience%20with%20AI%20as%20possible%20so%20they%20understand%20the%20technology's%20capabilities%20and%20its%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20throw%20AI%20at%20a%20problem%20and%20expect%20it%20to%20solve%20it%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Castillo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastillo%20said%20that%20he%20starts%20many%20of%20his%20courses%20by%20teaching%20students%20how%20to%20write%20business%20cases%20and%20frame%20them%20within%20an%20overall%20corporate%20strategy.%20They%20use%20analytics%20to%20inform%20their%20larger%20business%20strategies%2C%20and%20tools%20like%20AI%20act%20as%20their%20decision-making%20aids.%20The%20students%2C%20once%20hired%2C%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20making%20decisions%20and%20held%20accountable%2C%20not%20AI%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20lead%20AI%20rather%20than%20let%20it%20lead%20them.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20never%20know%20where%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Castillo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20d