%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20individuals%20generating%20small%20quantities%2C%20contact%20your%20nearest%20urban%20municipal%20body%20or%20health%20department%20to%20check%20if%20they%20have%20a%20tie-up%20with%20such%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20needs%20to%20change%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20that%20India%20needs%20a%20structured%20drug%20take-back%20system%20led%20by%20the%20government%20and%20supported%20by%20pharmacies%20and%20hospitals.%20Countries%20like%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20well-established%20systems%20where%20residents%20can%20return%20unused%20medicines%20at%20designated%20collection%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20has%20become%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20implement%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fkerala-to-launch-first-ever-project-on-collection-disposal-of-expired-medicines%2Farticleshow%2F118375784.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98nPROUD%E2%80%99%20project%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20to%20scientifically%20collect%20and%20safely%20dispose%20of%20expired%20and%20unused%20medicines.%20Launched%20by%20the%20State%20Drugs%20Control%20Department%2C%20the%20initiative%20%E2%80%98nPROUD%E2%80%99%20(New%20Programme%20for%20Removal%20of%20Unused%20Drugs)%20will%20facilitate%20the%20collection%20of%20unused%20medicines%20from%20households%20and%20ensure%20their%20proper%20disposal%20at%20designated%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20awareness%20is%20key.%20Pharmacists%2C%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20and%20citizens%20must%20be%20informed%20about%20the%20environmental%20and%20health%20hazards%20of%20improper%20medicine%20disposal.%20Educational%20institutions%20like%20Vivekananda%20Education%20Society%20(VES)%20College%20of%20Pharmacy%20are%20already%20trying%20to%20spread%20this%20message%20through%20student-led%20outreach%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20each%20of%20us%20makes%20the%20effort%20to%20dispose%20of%20medicines%20the%20right%20way%2C%20we%20contribute%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20healthier%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20next%20time%20you%20open%20your%20medicine%20drawer%20and%20spot%20an%20expired%20tablet%20strip%2C%20remember%3A%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Saumya%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pfizer.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fhow_to_dispose_of_unused_medicine_responsibly_to_protect_the_environment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Dispose%20of%20Unused%20Medicine%20Responsibly%20to%20Protect%20the%20Environment%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Pfizer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvespharmacy.ves.ac.in%2F284-nr%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIf%2520there%2520is%2520no%2520drug%2520take%252Dback%2520location%2520nearby%2520and%2Cof%2520water%2520make%2520an%2520Ocean%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20I%20dispose%20unused%20or%20expired%20medicine%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20VES%20College%20of%20Pharmacy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fwhat-should-you-do-with-leftover-medicines%2Fphotostory%2F95142124.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20should%20you%20do%20with%20leftover%20medicines%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20