Fgorai-mangrove-park-in-mumbai-opening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esprawling%20mangrove%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20quietly%20flourishing%20within%20the%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pirojshanagar%20Township%20in%20Vikhroli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%20thousands%20of%20acres%2C%20this%20green%20lung%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20offering%20a%20cooler%20commute%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20regulating%20microclimates%2C%20filtering%20air%20and%20water%2C%20and%20shielding%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20shoreline%20from%20floods%20and%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%2C%20rainfall%20in%20this%20pocket%20is%20often%20heavier%20and%20gentler%2C%20absorbed%20by%20the%20thirsty%20roots%20of%20the%20mangroves.%20The%20Creekside%20Colony%2C%20one%20of%20three%20residential%20clusters%20near%20the%20forest%2C%20enjoys%20what%20residents%20call%20a%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20climate%E2%80%99%E2%80%94cleaner%20air%2C%20less%20heat%2C%20and%20an%20occasional%20chorus%20of%20birdsong.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20city%20constantly%20battling%20rising%20temperatures%2C%20waterlogging%2C%20and%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20just%20one%20visible%20outcome%20of%20a%20much%20deeper%2C%20long-term%20commitment.%20Since%20they%20acquired%20the%20land%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20has%20chosen%20to%20preserve%20and%20protect%20this%20mangrove%20ecosystem%2C%20not%20as%20a%20CSR%20project%2C%20not%20for%20branding%2C%20and%20not%20as%20a%20compliance%20tick%20box%E2%80%94but%20as%20an%20act%20of%20belief%E2%80%94a%20belief%20that%20business%20and%20biodiversity%20can%20exist%20harmoniously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20even%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20concrete%20jungle%2C%20a%20forest%20can%20be%20nurtured%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20care%20enough%20to%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20%E2%80%98wasteland%E2%80%