%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Natural%20climate%20defence%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20intensifying%20monsoons%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20flood%20risk%20grows%20each%20year.%20Mangroves%20act%20like%20sponges%2C%20absorbing%20excess%20rainwater%20and%20buffering%20coastlines%20from%20storm%20surges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%E2%80%99ve%20realised%20through%20research%20is%20that%20mangroves%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20stormwater%20drainage.%20When%20natural%20outlets%20are%20clogged%20or%20encroached%20upon%2C%20water%20can%E2%80%99t%20flow%20out%20into%20the%20sea%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20Mumbai%20floods.%20Mangroves%20help%20maintain%20that%20crucial%20flow%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Joshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20A%20powerful%20carbon%20sink%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20store%20carbon%20at%20rates%20far%20greater%20than%20terrestrial%20forests.%20Godrej%E2%80%99s%20mangroves%20alone%20have%20sequestered%202.3%20million%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%2C%20continuing%20to%20lock%20away%2060%2C000%20tonnes%20annually%2C%20%E2%80%94%20a%20critical%20contribution%20in%20a%20city%20battling%20air%20pollution%20and%20rising%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Lifelines%20for%20biodiversity%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20ecosystems%20support%20over%20500%20documented%20species%2C%20from%20kingfishers%20to%20vulnerable%20raptors%20like%20the%20steppe%20eagle%20and%20even%20golden%20jackals.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20food%20web%20here%20is%20deeply%20interlinked.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20even%20had%20migratory%20birds%20return%20after%20years%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20something%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20the%20expert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t