%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173043.061_11zon-1749104266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173043.061_11zon-1749104266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173043.061_11zon-1749104266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173043.061_11zon-1749104266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173043.061_11zon-1749104266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444558%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETackling%20solid%20waste%20and%20greywater%20has%20become%20essential%20to%20protect%20these%20mangroves.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20troubling%20is%20declining%20water%20quality%2C%20fuelled%20by%20greywater%20discharge%20and%20untreated%20runoff%20from%20nearby%20human%20settlements.%20Already%20operating%20in%20harsh%2C%20saline%2C%20and%20shifting%20tidal%20conditions%2C%20mangroves%20are%20now%20burdened%20by%20pollutants%20that%20push%20sensitive%20species%20to%20the%20brink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMangrove%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3EAvicennia%20marina%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20adapted%2C%20but%20others%20are%20disappearing%20from%20urban%20coastlines%20altogether%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%E2%80%99s%20the%20pressure%20of%20urban%20expansion.%20As%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20population%20grows%2C%20natural%20ecosystems%2C%20often%20dismissed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunused%E2%80%9D%2C%20become%20prime%20targets%20for%20development.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20areas%20need%20to%20be%20highlighted%20and%20protected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20urges.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20open%20land%3B%20they%20provide%20vital%20ecosystem%20services%20that%20cities%20depend%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMangroves%20may%20seem%20hardy%2C%20but%20beyond%20a%20point%2C%20degradation%20is%20irreversible%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20within%20a%20protected%20campus%2C%20the%20Godrej%20team%20finds%20itself%20constantly%20defending%20boundaries%20and%20biodiversity%2C%20holding%20the%20line%20against%20a%20tide%20of%20indifference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMangroves%20do%20what%20concrete%20can%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20Wetlands%20Management%20Team%20continues%20to%20delve%20into%20conservation%2C%20and%20their%20efforts%20are%20paying%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mangroves%20act%20as%20a%20carbon%20sink%2C%20flood%20barrier%2C%20and%20bio-filtration%20system.%20It%E2%80%99s%20living%2C%20breathing%20climate%20infrastructure.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20underrated%20climate%20infrastructure%20we%20have.%20And%20yet%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20built%20over%20much%20of%20it%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20living%20example%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20possible%20when%20cities%20put%20nature%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Godrej%20has%20built%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20conservation%20story%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20replicable%20blueprint%20for%20urban%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rapidly%20expanding%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20pressure%20to%20convert%20every%20patch%20of%20green%20into%20grey%20is%20immense.%20Yet%20mangroves%20remind%20us%20that%20not%20all%20%E2%80%98vacant%E2%80%99%20land%20is%20unproductive%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20it%20is%20quietly%20doing%20the%20critical%20work%20that%20keeps%20cities%20liveable.%20From%20reducing%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect%20and%20absorbing%20CO%E2%82%82%20to%20preventing%20floods%20and%20protecting%20coastal%20infrastructure%2C%20mangroves%20offer%20nature-based%20solutions%20to%20urban%20challenges%20that%20concrete%20can%E2%80%99t%20fix.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20could%20protect%20this%20in%20the%2080s%20%E2%80%94%20before%20ESG%2C%20before%20climate%20anxiety%20%E2%80%94%20then%20others%20can%20do%20it%20now.%20It%E2%80%99s%20never%20too%20late%20to%20let%20nature%20breathe%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20stop%20looking%20at%20natural%20ecosystems%20as%20land%20banks%20and%20start%20seeing%20them%20as%20living%20infrastructure%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejashree%20Joshi.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20a%20luxury%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20a%20necessity%20for%20future-ready%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173308.012-1749104316.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22people%20involved%20in%20the%20awareness%20programme%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173308.012-1749104316.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173308.012-1749104316-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173308.012-1749104316-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173308.012-1749104316-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T173308.012-1749104316-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444559%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20employees%20at%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20also%20provide%20an%20induction%20on%20mangrove%20conservation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20conservation%20approach%20also%20factors%20in%20education%20and%20behavioural%20change%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20pillars%20of%20sustainable%20planning.%20Through%20community%20walks%2C%20employee%20engagement%2C%20and%20large-scale%20outreach%2C%20Godrej%20is%20shaping%20how%20citizens%20perceive%20and%20value%20natural%20ecosystems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20has%20also%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20UNDP%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20through%20its%20designation%20as%20an%20OECM%20(Other%20Effective%20Area-Based%20Conservation%20Measure)%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20privately%20held%20lands%20in%20India%20to%20receive%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20city%20where%20every%20square%20metre%20is%20monetised%2C%20Godrej%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358648%2Fmangrove-conservationists-ayush-sarda-murukesan-prasenjit-mandal-coasts-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elet%20the%20forest%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rather%20than%20build%2C%20is%20both%20radical%20and%20reassuring%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20blueprint%20for%20what%20climate-resilient%20urban%20development%20can%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20something%20we%20brag%20about.%20We%20just%20do%20it%20%E2%80%94%20year%20after%20year%2C%20species%20by%20species%2C%20with%20science%20and%20soul%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20maybe%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20it%20matter%20even%20more.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20loud%2C%20not%20performative.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20quiet%20commitment%20that%E2%80%99s%20grown%20into%20a%20sanctuary%20for%20biodiversity%2C%20a%20shield%20for%20the%20city%2C%20and%20a%20powerful%20reminder%20that%20climate%20leadership%20starts%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20with%20mud%20on%20your%20boots%20and%20mangroves%20at%20your%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20a%20city%20fighting%20to%20breathe%2C%20this%20is%20where%20the%20air%20still%20smells%20of%20salt%20and%20leaves.%20And%20if%20we%E2%80%99re%20lucky%2C%20it%20always%20will!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%20Castelino%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Godrej%20Enterprises%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGroup%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749117225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T172116.524-1749102854.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D444536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20city%20where%20every%20inch%20of%20land%20is%20built%20upon%2C%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20chose%20to%20protect%20a%20forest%20instead.%20For%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20nurtured%20acres%20of%20mangroves%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20protecting%20biodiversity%2C%20preventing%20floods%2C%20and%20building%20a%20climate-resilient%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F444536%2Fmangrove-conservation-godrej-vikhroli-mumbai-species-biodiversity%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Jugaad%20Culture%20Through%20Stunning%20Photos%3A%20Inside%20the%20Lives%20of%20Those%20Who%20Fix%2C%20Reuse%20%26amp%3B%20Reinvent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20Sunday%20morning%20in%20May%20when%20I%20set%20out%20on%20a%20photo%20walk%20with%20my%20best%20friend%20through%20the%20old%20lanes%20of%20Lucknow.%20Having%20recently%20relocated%2C%20this%20was%20my%20first%20time%20back%20in%20the%20old%20city%20and%20just%20the%20thought%20of%20seeing%20its%20rustic%20monuments%2C%20crumbling%20bricks%2C%20and%20fading%20paint%20brought%20back%20memories%20of%20a%20slower%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time%20when%20people%20valued%20what%20they%20had%20and%20chose%20to%20repair%2C%20not%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20six%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20the%20shops%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F431994%2Flucknow-bioscope-sanatkada-begum-akhtar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucknow%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EChowk%20Bazaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20still%20shuttered%20as%20we%20set%20off%20on%20our%20little%20adventure%2C%20joined%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20like-minded%20folks%2C%20all%20curious%20and%20eager%20to%20freeze%20time%20through%20our%20lenses.%20As%20we%20walked%2C%20our%20organiser%20shared%20stories%20about%20the%20streets%2C%20including%20one%20about%20%3Cem%3EChor%20Bazaar%20(Thieves%E2%80%99%20Market)%20%3C%2Fem%3Enear%20Victoria%20Street.%20He%20told%20us%20it%20was%20once%20called%20%3Cem%3EShahi%20Bazaar%20(Royal%20Market)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20place%20where%20people%20still%20buy%20old%20clothes%2C%20second-hand%20watches%2C%20and%20even%20get%20their%20transistors%20repaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20moment%20reminded%20me%20of%20how%20deeply%20ingrained%3Cem%3E%20jugaad%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fem%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20making%20do%20with%20what%E2%80%99s%20available%20%E2%80%94%20is%20in%20our%20culture.%20My%20mind%20drifted%20to%20memories%20of%20my%20mother%20taking%20my%20worn-out%20shoes%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Emochi%20(cobbler)%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20stitching%2C%20or%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebartan%20wala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(utensil%20seller%20ot%20trader)%20who%20would%20roam%20our%20neighbourhood%2C%20trading%20old%20utensils%20for%20money.%20All%20signs%20of%20a%20quiet%20culture%20of%20repair%2C%20reuse%2C%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flab